<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Security Update for Microsoft Office Publisher 2007 (KB980470)</Title><Description>A security vulnerability exists in Microsoft Office Publisher 2007 that could allow arbitrary code to run when a maliciously modified file is opened. This update resolves that vulnerability.</Description><MoreInfoUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/kb/980470</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com/?LN=en-us</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>